It is really gratifying

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.000
to come to Melbourne

00:00:05.679 --> 00:00:07.679
I came here

00:00:08.124 --> 00:00:11.602
because somebody who had come to Sydney

00:00:12.983 --> 00:00:16.896
and said that "Mother, you must come to Melbourne.

00:00:18.140 --> 00:00:19.026
We need you."

00:00:22.047 --> 00:00:24.623
When I came here for some other purpose,

00:00:27.196 --> 00:00:31.103
I felt vibrations of Melbourne

00:00:32.522 --> 00:00:33.917
are really very good,

00:00:35.635 --> 00:00:38.440
and here it is quite possible

00:00:38.790 --> 00:00:40.790
that there maybe many seekers.

00:00:46.012 --> 00:00:48.012
It is really gratifying as I said

00:00:48.277 --> 00:00:49.706
to be here among you.

00:00:52.856 --> 00:00:55.844
It's a fact that the time has come

00:00:56.216 --> 00:00:58.690
for thousands and thousands and thousands

00:00:58.976 --> 00:01:00.976
and millions of them

00:01:02.587 --> 00:01:05.103
who are born as seekers on this earth,

00:01:06.351 --> 00:01:09.425
have to get their Realisation.

00:01:11.699 --> 00:01:13.699
They have to know their meaning.

00:01:14.370 --> 00:01:16.370
They have to know why

00:01:17.169 --> 00:01:21.628
why the nature has made them a human being from amoeba.

00:01:22.962 --> 00:01:24.962
What is the purpose of their life?

00:01:25.783 --> 00:01:28.595
Unless and until you find the purpose of your life

00:01:28.988 --> 00:01:30.988
you are not going to be happy.

00:01:31.830 --> 00:01:33.830
You are not going to be satisfied.

00:01:33.967 --> 00:01:35.666
You may try anything else.

00:01:36.059 --> 00:01:38.317
You may have one of those ego trips;

00:01:39.116 --> 00:01:43.190
you may have other trips like seeking money.

00:01:44.673 --> 00:01:49.028
You may have other things like going to drugs,

00:01:50.319 --> 00:01:51.510
alcoholism,

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:54.923
livercation, all kinds of things.

00:01:55.658 --> 00:01:58.723
But these things have not given any satisfaction,

00:02:00.056 --> 00:02:00.885
to anyone.

00:02:03.693 --> 00:02:05.693
You have to find out that Absolute,

00:02:06.834 --> 00:02:09.241
without which we are in confusion.

00:02:11.835 --> 00:02:13.835
That Absolute is within you.

00:02:15.681 --> 00:02:18.081
That's why Sahaja Yoga

00:02:18.837 --> 00:02:21.491
is as spontaneous thing, is a living thing.

00:02:22.354 --> 00:02:24.657
"Saha" means with, "Ja" means born.

00:02:25.157 --> 00:02:26.577
It is born with you,

00:02:27.205 --> 00:02:28.564
as in a seed

00:02:28.914 --> 00:02:32.240
all the maps of the seed that is going to manifest

00:02:33.616 --> 00:02:36.157
are built-in.

00:02:36.315 --> 00:02:38.315
In the same way within you,

00:02:40.973 --> 00:02:44.280
your Spirit and your Kundalini

00:02:44.438 --> 00:02:49.035
are all already existing there

00:02:49.578 --> 00:02:52.028
and they are just waiting for a chance

00:02:53.447 --> 00:02:55.618
to give you your Self-Realisation.

00:02:58.533 --> 00:03:04.388
Before telling you about the benefits of Self-Realisation,

00:03:06.063 --> 00:03:09.569
I have to tell you that you must keep your minds open

00:03:10.069 --> 00:03:14.191
as you would for any science lecture or any other lecture.

00:03:17.447 --> 00:03:19.447
There's no jugglery

00:03:20.567 --> 00:03:25.107
or there is no shopping, guru shopping in Sahaja Yoga.

00:03:26.547 --> 00:03:28.971
It is a happening, it’s an actualisation.

00:03:30.390 --> 00:03:33.108
It is within you. It’s a living force,

00:03:33.608 --> 00:03:38.348
like a flower becomes a fruit

00:03:39.745 --> 00:03:42.720
or an egg becomes a chick,

00:03:43.733 --> 00:03:47.619
you get your Realisation and you become a different personality,

00:03:47.628 --> 00:03:51.362
a new dimension of awareness grows into you

00:03:52.311 --> 00:03:55.223
and this new dimension of awareness

00:03:55.274 --> 00:03:56.695
is an actualisation,

00:03:57.024 --> 00:04:00.645
it's not just a mere words

00:04:01.145 --> 00:04:04.717
or any kind of a brainwashing.

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:08.225
It is an actualisation within you,

00:04:10.178 --> 00:04:12.801
which happens by which

00:04:13.301 --> 00:04:15.301
you start feeling

00:04:15.801 --> 00:04:17.801
the collective consciousness.

00:04:18.835 --> 00:04:22.341
You are a part and parcel of the whole,

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:23.655
so many have said it.

00:04:25.202 --> 00:04:26.376
We also believe in it

00:04:26.513 --> 00:04:28.753
that we are the part and parcel of the whole,

00:04:29.338 --> 00:04:31.682
but so far in our awareness,

00:04:32.503 --> 00:04:35.269
in our central nervous system, we have not felt that.

00:04:38.184 --> 00:04:40.827
So this is actually should happen to you.

00:04:45.088 --> 00:04:48.222
In this we have to accept,

00:04:49.192 --> 00:04:54.025
whatever is nourishing for our growth, after Realisation.

00:04:55.679 --> 00:04:58.082
Gradually you started accepting it

00:04:58.582 --> 00:05:00.582
and I'll tell you why it happens

00:05:02.214 --> 00:05:04.947
but the thing is in Sydney I found

00:05:05.447 --> 00:05:08.567
that people are extremely honest about their seeking

00:05:09.067 --> 00:05:11.983
and they really appreciated my honesty.

00:05:15.667 --> 00:05:17.667
This is a process

00:05:18.017 --> 00:05:20.275
which was built in since long within us.

00:05:21.578 --> 00:05:23.871
Here that you see different chakras.

00:05:24.371 --> 00:05:25.471
Are placed.

00:05:30.625 --> 00:05:33.385
Can you see? All right.

00:05:33.701 --> 00:05:37.130
These centres are placed within

00:05:38.889 --> 00:05:40.109
the human beings

00:05:41.886 --> 00:05:44.108
and they exist at subtle centers

00:05:45.557 --> 00:05:47.742
in the spinal cord and in the brain.

00:05:50.541 --> 00:05:53.970
These are called in Sanskrit language as chakras.

00:05:55.784 --> 00:05:58.523
These centres exist within us

00:05:59.187 --> 00:06:01.677
as milestones of our evolution.

00:06:02.615 --> 00:06:04.615
For example, the lowest chakra

00:06:05.115 --> 00:06:07.115
called as the Mooladdhara chakra,

00:06:07.615 --> 00:06:09.615
is the center,

00:06:11.447 --> 00:06:15.643
at that point we were carbon atoms. We were matter.

00:06:19.209 --> 00:06:22.424
At that point we were innocent. Matter is innocent.

00:06:24.201 --> 00:06:27.586
So the first thing that was created within us was innocence.

00:06:28.925 --> 00:06:31.515
This whole universe was created

00:06:33.037 --> 00:06:35.037
after innocence was created.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.800
This chakra is placed

00:06:40.300 --> 00:06:43.034
below the Kundalini, if you see it clearly.

00:06:43.881 --> 00:06:47.468
Kundalini is the pure power of desire.

00:06:48.315 --> 00:06:50.315
Pure power of desire.

00:06:50.815 --> 00:06:53.017
Whatever is pure we call it Holy.

00:06:53.937 --> 00:06:57.605
Is the Holy power of desire,

00:06:58.963 --> 00:07:00.963
which remains

00:07:02.850 --> 00:07:04.850
dormant.

00:07:09.365 --> 00:07:12.022
This power is the desire

00:07:12.668 --> 00:07:15.455
to be one with the Spirit.

00:07:17.141 --> 00:07:20.238
Without knowing the Spirit, you cannot know God.

00:07:22.125 --> 00:07:24.346
You are to be input to the mains.

00:07:25.704 --> 00:07:27.229
You are not yet put to the mains.

00:07:27.273 --> 00:07:29.437
For example, this instrument that we have made

00:07:30.247 --> 00:07:32.876
if it is not put to the mains, it has no meaning.

00:07:34.288 --> 00:07:36.288
So that has to happen.

00:07:36.788 --> 00:07:38.788
It's like the primule in the seed,

00:07:38.905 --> 00:07:40.905
a germinating power

00:07:41.715 --> 00:07:42.473
in the seed,

00:07:42.864 --> 00:07:46.087
that you have got this power, residual power

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:47.899
sleeping

00:07:48.581 --> 00:07:50.581
waiting for a moment

00:07:50.844 --> 00:07:52.246
when somebody

00:07:52.746 --> 00:07:55.259
who is authorised by the Divine

00:07:55.412 --> 00:07:56.354
and not

00:07:56.653 --> 00:07:59.164
by any organization or certificates

00:08:00.449 --> 00:08:01.869
that human beings give.

00:08:02.844 --> 00:08:05.618
But somebody, who himself is a Realised soul,

00:08:05.954 --> 00:08:07.954
as an enlightened person

00:08:08.454 --> 00:08:09.454
and he knows

00:08:11.304 --> 00:08:13.652
what is this power is,

00:08:16.506 --> 00:08:18.506
it waits for such a personality

00:08:19.900 --> 00:08:21.900
and then it awakens itself

00:08:22.035 --> 00:08:24.035
and you get your Self-Realisation.

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:29.820
It has to be spontaneous

00:08:29.919 --> 00:08:34.132
everything vital in life has to be spontaneous.

00:08:36.128 --> 00:08:39.345
The breathing that we have

00:08:40.575 --> 00:08:43.609
is so spontaneously going on

00:08:44.109 --> 00:08:48.196
that we take it for granted till it stops, or till we feel

00:08:49.718 --> 00:08:51.051
that we cannot breathe.

00:08:53.157 --> 00:08:55.157
If you have to go and read books,

00:08:55.274 --> 00:08:58.881
or putting some efforts to breathe,

00:08:59.381 --> 00:09:03.598
then how many of us could

00:09:04.098 --> 00:09:06.616
even exist for more than

00:09:07.481 --> 00:09:09.481
say five minutes?

00:09:11.404 --> 00:09:13.404
It is so vital

00:09:13.776 --> 00:09:16.256
is the culmination of our evolution

00:09:17.833 --> 00:09:22.296
and as the whole creation was created by the Divine,

00:09:23.453 --> 00:09:26.509
as you are also created by the Divine,

00:09:27.155 --> 00:09:31.428
this great happening is to be done by the Divine.

00:09:35.213 --> 00:09:37.213
Now some people asked me

00:09:37.286 --> 00:09:40.433
that can it not happen by itself to us.

00:09:41.424 --> 00:09:46.198
We do not know that at every stage of our evolution

00:09:47.104 --> 00:09:50.167
some aspect of God had to incarnate

00:09:50.795 --> 00:09:53.893
or some guidance had to come from the Divine,

00:09:55.782 --> 00:09:59.824
to give us a higher awareness.

00:10:01.350 --> 00:10:03.350
But specially at this time

00:10:03.700 --> 00:10:05.080
it is very important

00:10:05.409 --> 00:10:07.409
that somebody has to do it

00:10:07.909 --> 00:10:11.130
because you have reached a stage where,

00:10:12.314 --> 00:10:15.984
you have to know it in words,

00:10:16.762 --> 00:10:19.045
and Divine had to speak.

00:10:22.301 --> 00:10:26.456
It's a very common question that in,

00:10:26.465 --> 00:10:28.465
I think people are ego orientated,

00:10:28.901 --> 00:10:31.574
they said, "Why you Mother?" I said you better be there!

00:10:32.245 --> 00:10:35.043
I’ll be very happy if you could do it

00:10:35.778 --> 00:10:39.180
because I am a happily married woman,

00:10:39.894 --> 00:10:41.894
I don't need anything from anyone,

00:10:42.394 --> 00:10:44.394
I have to just give

00:10:44.894 --> 00:10:50.447
but if you can do my work, I will be very happy to retire.

00:10:52.699 --> 00:10:55.744
It's very easy to say, "why you?" I mean you should ask

00:10:55.757 --> 00:10:58.271
God why He gave me these powers?

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:01.160
But they are there,

00:11:01.392 --> 00:11:05.331
but one need not feel hurt about it so much also.

00:11:05.539 --> 00:11:08.282
After all you have some many powers which I don't have.

00:11:08.782 --> 00:11:10.782
For example, I don't know how to drive,

00:11:11.282 --> 00:11:12.364
really I don't know.

00:11:12.669 --> 00:11:13.870
I don’t know many things,

00:11:13.932 --> 00:11:16.626
even I don't know how to open ordinary cans

00:11:17.248 --> 00:11:19.965
but if I know how to open the Kundalini

00:11:20.684 --> 00:11:22.684
why should it hurt your ego?

00:11:23.574 --> 00:11:25.574
And why should you feel bad

00:11:25.733 --> 00:11:28.485
because I have to really work day in day out.

00:11:30.396 --> 00:11:32.396
To do this work,

00:11:33.529 --> 00:11:35.529
it’s something just a gift to you.

00:11:35.810 --> 00:11:37.810
There is no shopping;

00:11:38.091 --> 00:11:40.091
you can't pay for it.

00:11:40.372 --> 00:11:41.831
It is beyond,

00:11:42.818 --> 00:11:44.818
your control.

00:11:45.318 --> 00:11:50.459
To conceive God, you have to see, as the reality is.

00:11:51.616 --> 00:11:53.640
You have to give up your conceptions.

00:11:53.702 --> 00:11:56.819
Supposing I had conceived a hall

00:11:57.319 --> 00:11:59.319
before seeing this,

00:11:59.478 --> 00:12:01.478
I would have had funny ideas

00:12:02.197 --> 00:12:03.642
but after seeing it

00:12:03.680 --> 00:12:06.570
only I really know what it is.

00:12:07.386 --> 00:12:08.559
In the same way

00:12:09.059 --> 00:12:10.363
people have written books,

00:12:11.033 --> 00:12:13.033
thousands of books they have written

00:12:13.533 --> 00:12:16.163
or even millions of books they have written, so what to do?

00:12:17.223 --> 00:12:18.544
If they have written the books,

00:12:18.582 --> 00:12:21.309
have they given you any Self-Realisation?

00:12:23.852 --> 00:12:26.445
Have they given you that experience

00:12:26.945 --> 00:12:29.490
of the absolute by which you know yourself,

00:12:29.990 --> 00:12:32.985
you know your centres and you know the centre of others

00:12:33.485 --> 00:12:36.217
and you start manifesting your own powers.

00:12:37.739 --> 00:12:39.911
You become the master of your powers.

00:12:42.698 --> 00:12:47.110
This is what should be the criteria of your seeking.

00:12:48.437 --> 00:12:52.825
Why should you be identified with anything else but yourself?

00:12:54.225 --> 00:12:55.633
Because I get people

00:12:55.865 --> 00:12:57.940
belonging to this cult or this group

00:12:58.002 --> 00:13:00.002
or this religion or this and that.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:05.184
But you must understand

00:13:05.684 --> 00:13:07.684
that you are not here

00:13:07.916 --> 00:13:09.916
to be pleader for any one of them.

00:13:10.684 --> 00:13:13.102
I mean you pay them to be their pleader

00:13:14.794 --> 00:13:18.411
or to be their lawyers or solicitors, whatever you may call it.

00:13:21.003 --> 00:13:24.442
But you should really try to honestly seek the truth

00:13:24.942 --> 00:13:26.653
and ask for this truth

00:13:27.028 --> 00:13:29.028
and then only you will get the truth.

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:32.720
So first thing one should understand

00:13:32.952 --> 00:13:34.952
that you cannot purchase Divine.

00:13:35.671 --> 00:13:38.058
You cannot pay for it, it is an insult,

00:13:39.580 --> 00:13:40.796
it is an insult.

00:13:42.877 --> 00:13:46.048
And secondly you cannot put in effort for that.

00:13:46.889 --> 00:13:48.352
When you have to sprout a seed

00:13:48.365 --> 00:13:50.365
what do you do? You put it in the Mother Earth,

00:13:50.914 --> 00:13:53.381
and she sprouts by itself spontaneously.

00:13:54.100 --> 00:13:55.598
It has got that force in it,

00:13:55.660 --> 00:13:57.859
only you have to put it to the Mother Earth.

00:13:58.967 --> 00:14:01.410
And the Mother Earth by her warmth

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:03.910
germinates the seed.

00:14:04.994 --> 00:14:07.240
Do you get angry with the Mother Earth for that,

00:14:07.278 --> 00:14:08.885
that, why must you do that?

00:14:11.137 --> 00:14:13.357
If she has to do it, she has to do it.

00:14:13.857 --> 00:14:16.077
Whatever the sun has to do has to do,

00:14:16.577 --> 00:14:18.577
and whatever you have to do, you can do

00:14:18.907 --> 00:14:20.907
and whatever the animals have to do, they do.

00:14:24.326 --> 00:14:25.676
If we understand that

00:14:25.714 --> 00:14:28.282
we have not yet achieved what we wanted to,

00:14:31.969 --> 00:14:33.969
then you will realise

00:14:34.761 --> 00:14:36.761
that there is a very little gap.

00:14:38.453 --> 00:14:40.453
The Kundalini awakening takes

00:14:41.342 --> 00:14:42.981
split of a second,

00:14:44.162 --> 00:14:49.467
but its rising may take more time in certain people

00:14:50.575 --> 00:14:55.131
because of blockages in the centre

00:14:55.972 --> 00:14:59.432
or maybe some imbalances within us.

00:15:01.708 --> 00:15:04.303
In short I will try to tell you

00:15:04.730 --> 00:15:07.286
what is the Kundalini and what is this picture about.

00:15:09.002 --> 00:15:11.002
I hope you have got some books with you,

00:15:11.161 --> 00:15:13.546
you can also open and see for yourself.

00:15:14.046 --> 00:15:17.562
Those who haven't got books can also get from them,

00:15:18.767 --> 00:15:22.181
it will be easier to understand it.

00:15:24.554 --> 00:15:28.237
At the back of the book you will find a nice chart.

00:15:40.146 --> 00:15:42.849
Firstly you have to be honest about your seeking,

00:15:44.054 --> 00:15:47.271
absolutely honest about it then everything will work out.

00:15:50.666 --> 00:15:54.064
Now here you see this chart

00:15:54.564 --> 00:15:56.564
is the first center

00:15:57.064 --> 00:15:59.209
called as the Mooladhara chakra, as I said,

00:16:00.585 --> 00:16:01.691
and the sacrum.

00:16:02.556 --> 00:16:04.847
See the meaning of the word sacrum means sacred.

00:16:06.077 --> 00:16:09.224
Sacrum is the bone in which the Kundalini is there.

00:16:11.865 --> 00:16:14.282
I would like you to see from the top

00:16:15.877 --> 00:16:19.512
this blue color balloon like structure

00:16:19.866 --> 00:16:21.866
comes down up to the first chakra.

00:16:26.672 --> 00:16:27.728
Now this,

00:16:32.899 --> 00:16:36.686
represents a subtle force within us,

00:16:38.743 --> 00:16:41.226
which is the power of desire.

00:16:43.623 --> 00:16:45.623
It manifests outside

00:16:46.123 --> 00:16:48.123
the left sympathetic nervous system.

00:16:50.496 --> 00:16:53.012
This is the emotional side of a human being.

00:16:53.512 --> 00:16:54.841
It is not only emotional.

00:16:59.112 --> 00:17:02.323
This is the one that

00:17:02.823 --> 00:17:04.823
takes conditionings

00:17:07.293 --> 00:17:08.411
within itself

00:17:08.473 --> 00:17:11.495
when we say "Don't do that, don't do that, don't do that"

00:17:16.009 --> 00:17:19.259
and creates by its activity

00:17:20.148 --> 00:17:24.107
a balloon like structure called as superego

00:17:24.607 --> 00:17:26.607
which is in Sanskrit called as mana.

00:17:28.275 --> 00:17:33.007
So this is the power of mana, of manashakti.

00:17:33.430 --> 00:17:35.101
English language is a little

00:17:35.236 --> 00:17:37.236
confused, when you say mental cases

00:17:37.468 --> 00:17:40.014
you do not mean, the mental cases

00:17:40.149 --> 00:17:42.597
that has something to do with the

00:17:42.756 --> 00:17:44.357
mind which thinks.

00:17:44.857 --> 00:17:46.471
But when you say mental cases,

00:17:46.776 --> 00:17:50.060
you mean to say that they are the people who suffer

00:17:50.292 --> 00:17:52.292
from emotional problems.

00:17:53.741 --> 00:17:55.175
It's a little confused thing

00:17:55.894 --> 00:17:57.894
but in psychology

00:17:58.954 --> 00:18:01.274
it is very nicely described by Jung,

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:03.065
who was a realised soul himself,

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:05.238
the superego

00:18:06.857 --> 00:18:09.202
and the ID part is this

00:18:11.089 --> 00:18:13.430
power by which we

00:18:15.414 --> 00:18:17.972
get all our conditionings within us

00:18:18.326 --> 00:18:20.326
and we pass it to our past.

00:18:20.996 --> 00:18:23.317
Beyond this area on the left-hand side

00:18:24.206 --> 00:18:26.206
lies beyond the subconscious,

00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:30.085
the collective sub-conscious, all that is dead,

