and do not have them in your life, it's alright.

00:52:00.127 --> 00:52:02.509
But if you are taking

00:52:02.774 --> 00:52:05.896
interest in them as well as fighting with them morning till evening,

00:52:06.033 --> 00:52:07.712
then you catch on this heart chakra.

00:52:09.451 --> 00:52:13.066
I would say that in this respect Indians are sensible people.

00:52:14.143 --> 00:52:17.619
They are very sensible that they keep their parents all right.

00:52:18.226 --> 00:52:19.841
And the parents are also yet

00:52:19.985 --> 00:52:22.469
very sensible people. They love their children, they give

00:52:22.478 --> 00:52:24.478
everything that they have to the children,

00:52:24.615 --> 00:52:30.271
and children start really loving their parents,

00:52:30.429 --> 00:52:32.429
till they die they look after them.

00:52:33.933 --> 00:52:36.387
The result of that is of course very bad,

00:52:36.887 --> 00:52:40.274
because here in all the western countries the parents

00:52:40.475 --> 00:52:43.299
are still in a bridal mood, I mean they are brides

00:52:43.991 --> 00:52:45.991
and the bridegrooms you see

00:52:46.491 --> 00:52:49.709
they never become old enough to be parents.

00:52:49.740 --> 00:52:51.587
Seen even an eighty year old man you will find

00:52:51.595 --> 00:52:53.765
marry an eighteen year old girl. I mean

00:52:53.816 --> 00:52:55.816
it's a thing going on all the time. God knows

00:52:56.316 --> 00:52:58.316
what sort of intelligence is that?

00:52:59.008 --> 00:53:01.500
But with all that happening

00:53:01.658 --> 00:53:03.658
poor children do not know

00:53:03.923 --> 00:53:05.605
which parents to be chosen.

00:53:06.105 --> 00:53:08.427
And the last judgement has started, now what to do?

00:53:09.269 --> 00:53:11.269
Now you place yourself in their places

00:53:11.342 --> 00:53:12.674
and think what would you do

00:53:12.768 --> 00:53:14.938
when you know such crazy parents that today

00:53:14.947 --> 00:53:16.712
they are together, tomorrow they are divorced.

00:53:17.212 --> 00:53:19.082
On the streets they will be kissing,

00:53:19.347 --> 00:53:20.647
hugging each other,

00:53:21.147 --> 00:53:24.459
doing all kind of nonsensical thing. Very embarrassing also,

00:53:25.579 --> 00:53:26.745
and if you ask them where are you

00:53:26.796 --> 00:53:28.796
going they say they are going to the divorce case.

00:53:32.672 --> 00:53:36.248
These kinds of absurdities are taking place and because of that

00:53:36.748 --> 00:53:38.748
children don't want to get birth

00:53:39.974 --> 00:53:41.824
in all these places; England,

00:53:41.851 --> 00:53:44.452
Germany, Switzerland, everywhere.

00:53:45.358 --> 00:53:49.441
The birth rate is towards the minus side.

00:53:49.941 --> 00:53:51.941
In Germany especially, West Germany

00:53:52.227 --> 00:53:54.468
and East Germany of all the things

00:53:54.519 --> 00:53:57.707
people give so much money that a woman if she produces

00:53:57.780 --> 00:54:01.062
three children she earns more money than their Prime Minister.

00:54:01.562 --> 00:54:03.562
But still women don't want to produce.

00:54:04.062 --> 00:54:06.839
They want to be free, independent, they don't want to be mothers.

00:54:07.617 --> 00:54:09.940
As a result this poor India

00:54:09.991 --> 00:54:12.856
has to accommodate for all the children born today

00:54:14.296 --> 00:54:17.582
and we are blamed for over population,

00:54:18.082 --> 00:54:20.718
now what to do? We have to bear the load.

00:54:24.017 --> 00:54:26.622
So also it is your responsibility

00:54:27.015 --> 00:54:29.299
to see if you do not produce children

00:54:29.350 --> 00:54:31.437
at least those who are producing children

00:54:31.638 --> 00:54:35.229
have some compassion for them

00:54:35.387 --> 00:54:37.474
and have some understanding.

00:54:37.504 --> 00:54:39.976
Do not blame them. Oh everybody tells me,

00:54:40.155 --> 00:54:42.802
what about your problem of population.

00:54:43.708 --> 00:54:47.295
I tell them now who is responsible for our population

00:54:49.291 --> 00:54:52.391
because in that country even if you have fourteen children,

00:54:52.891 --> 00:54:54.891
they love all their children that are there.

00:54:55.989 --> 00:54:59.429
They are not so ego-orientated that their hearts are not closed,

00:55:00.420 --> 00:55:02.420
they are not so unemotional,

00:55:03.198 --> 00:55:07.317
anybody who has no child will go to

00:55:07.368 --> 00:55:08.916
all the holy places

00:55:09.587 --> 00:55:12.084
and ask for blessings that they should get children,

00:55:13.161 --> 00:55:14.222
to get a child

00:55:14.231 --> 00:55:17.785
is such a blessing in India and child is such an important thing.

00:55:20.123 --> 00:55:22.530
But the mistake they are committing

00:55:22.581 --> 00:55:25.577
is just the other than yours.

00:55:26.376 --> 00:55:28.676
The mistake in those developing countries

00:55:28.706 --> 00:55:31.559
is that they do not believe that God Almighty

00:55:31.653 --> 00:55:34.438
is the One who is going to look after your well being.

00:55:35.152 --> 00:55:37.354
They don't believe in the power of their Father,

00:55:37.427 --> 00:55:39.588
so they do the crime against the Father or

00:55:39.597 --> 00:55:41.047
you can say the sin against the Father.

00:55:41.782 --> 00:55:44.314
When you don't believe in the capacity of your Father,

00:55:46.160 --> 00:55:49.579
so there is bribery, corruption, all sorts of things going on, you know

00:55:49.844 --> 00:55:52.941
cutting corners and money and all those things go on.

00:55:54.125 --> 00:55:55.866
Still in India I would not say that

00:55:56.772 --> 00:56:00.529
ordinary people are dishonest. I mean our bureaucrats may be, our

00:56:00.751 --> 00:56:03.666
politicians may be and business people may be. But

00:56:03.781 --> 00:56:05.781
ordinary people are very honest in India.

00:56:07.798 --> 00:56:09.047
But this is what happens.

00:56:10.055 --> 00:56:12.688
On the other side, you see supposing

00:56:13.188 --> 00:56:15.589
an Indian comes to your house, be careful

00:56:16.635 --> 00:56:20.108
he may run away with anything that you have in the house, anything,

00:56:20.608 --> 00:56:22.907
see, but

00:56:23.030 --> 00:56:25.842
if an American comes to your house, be careful about your wife.

00:56:27.641 --> 00:56:30.063
He may run away with your wife or with your daughter.

00:56:31.467 --> 00:56:34.990
Or say an Englishman comes he'll do it in a subtler way

00:56:35.490 --> 00:56:36.583
because he's a scholar.

00:56:37.893 --> 00:56:40.659
So he reads some poetry to your wife

00:56:40.971 --> 00:56:42.722
and in the night you find she is missing.

00:56:46.988 --> 00:56:50.042
This is fundamental, I mean the wife

00:56:50.467 --> 00:56:52.599
who runs away like this creates problem

00:56:53.965 --> 00:56:55.965
fundamentally for the household.

00:56:56.653 --> 00:56:58.653
Just think in a house,

00:56:59.022 --> 00:57:02.989
where there are children, there is husband, kitchen

00:57:03.489 --> 00:57:06.271
and all the places, everybody sleeping nicely,

00:57:06.771 --> 00:57:08.257
early in the morning they find

00:57:08.286 --> 00:57:11.505
that the main pole of the house is missing and the whole thing is collapsed.

00:57:12.250 --> 00:57:15.595
What will happen to the children, nobody thinks.

00:57:17.460 --> 00:57:18.604
Nobody understands

00:57:19.104 --> 00:57:21.707
or they think they are being in love

00:57:22.358 --> 00:57:23.503
so they must go.

00:57:24.210 --> 00:57:27.457
Men do the same. I mean there is no difference between men and women.

00:57:29.577 --> 00:57:32.990
But this is the sin against the Mother

00:57:36.089 --> 00:57:39.453
that the women have to be respectable and respected.

00:57:41.874 --> 00:57:45.365
Housewives’ position is within us

00:57:45.413 --> 00:57:47.413
here on the left hand side, nabhi

00:57:48.666 --> 00:57:50.171
and if a housewife,

00:57:50.332 --> 00:57:52.654
the deity of housewife, is not in our house,

00:57:52.740 --> 00:57:55.027
not that the woman but the housewife,

00:57:57.335 --> 00:57:59.335
then our spleen goes out.

00:58:01.229 --> 00:58:04.606
We get, children get crazy,

00:58:05.106 --> 00:58:07.903
why is there in-disciplined. Somebody asked me today

00:58:07.951 --> 00:58:12.632
what happens to the people like who try to kill Reagan?

00:58:13.149 --> 00:58:15.149
I said, ask his mother.

00:58:17.043 --> 00:58:20.126
She must be after the life of the child, morning till evening

00:58:20.626 --> 00:58:23.910
and that's why he's taking action,

00:58:24.033 --> 00:58:26.448
or is a reaction of what has happened to him.

00:58:27.664 --> 00:58:31.052
How do these complications arise

00:58:31.552 --> 00:58:33.552
has a basis in the family

00:58:34.542 --> 00:58:37.468
in the nest, that is your house.

00:58:39.437 --> 00:58:41.437
You have to live in the nest

00:58:42.427 --> 00:58:44.427
as a father and a mother

00:58:44.927 --> 00:58:46.390
looking after your children.

00:58:47.323 --> 00:58:49.970
Children are the most important things

00:58:51.091 --> 00:58:53.821
in the whole world for human beings.

00:58:57.541 --> 00:58:59.731
Let the politics go to hell,

00:58:59.817 --> 00:59:02.328
and let the economics take its own course,

00:59:02.828 --> 00:59:04.086
but children

00:59:04.812 --> 00:59:07.618
are to be looked after, that's your primary duty.

00:59:09.380 --> 00:59:11.380
But in India we go to the other end,

00:59:11.673 --> 00:59:13.901
when we start look after our children we don't mind

00:59:13.930 --> 00:59:15.930
selling our countries also in the name of children.

00:59:18.897 --> 00:59:20.897
But we live with two extremes I feel,

00:59:20.926 --> 00:59:22.604
the sin against the Mother

00:59:22.727 --> 00:59:24.727
and the sin against the Father.

00:59:27.204 --> 00:59:29.204
When we sin against the Mother

00:59:30.231 --> 00:59:32.974
as Australians, as I am now an Australian,

00:59:33.079 --> 00:59:35.079
let us face what happens to us.

00:59:39.364 --> 00:59:42.538
Absolutely we are emotionally blackmailed by ourselves.

00:59:44.142 --> 00:59:47.267
We torture ourselves, we live with artificial things.

00:59:48.407 --> 00:59:51.312
Like if a wife

00:59:51.812 --> 00:59:54.416
wants to run away with another man

00:59:55.161 --> 00:59:58.770
we will even go to get a honeymoon ticket for her

00:59:59.025 --> 01:00:01.982
because we are very considerate good husbands.

01:00:03.518 --> 01:00:06.332
Same thing with the wives if she finds that the husband

01:00:06.381 --> 01:00:08.381
is interested in another woman,

01:00:08.448 --> 01:00:10.448
she should not be jealous.

01:00:10.948 --> 01:00:16.842
In Sahaja Yoga this is not very much appreciated.

01:00:17.681 --> 01:00:20.465
Husband has to behave, like a husband. He should make his wife

01:00:20.532 --> 01:00:21.371
run the house.

01:00:22.022 --> 01:00:24.022
And the woman has to be a woman.

01:00:25.897 --> 01:00:27.897
She must see to it that

01:00:28.246 --> 01:00:30.246
no danger is brought to the children.

01:00:31.254 --> 01:00:34.409
We have no business to hurt anyone like this

01:00:34.721 --> 01:00:36.721
and we do not know how much we hurt,

01:00:37.221 --> 01:00:39.221
we give cancers to our wives and husbands.

01:00:40.324 --> 01:00:42.324
We give all kinds of horrible diseases,

01:00:42.692 --> 01:00:45.642
mental tortures we make them mad, by our

01:00:46.330 --> 01:00:48.330
mad, capricious,

01:00:50.111 --> 01:00:54.674
very shallow, understanding of our emotions.

01:00:56.812 --> 01:00:59.661
A one man starts going to another woman,

01:01:00.161 --> 01:01:01.567
then he goes to another woman,

01:01:01.747 --> 01:01:03.306
then to ten women he goes

01:01:03.392 --> 01:01:05.106
and then ten men go to ten women

01:01:05.192 --> 01:01:08.543
and end up in a lunatic asylum or

01:01:08.779 --> 01:01:12.547
in the orphanage. I have seen in England we had a neighbor

01:01:12.708 --> 01:01:16.116
who had a very huge house, he died, he was an old man

01:01:16.258 --> 01:01:17.315
and you'd be surprised

01:01:17.815 --> 01:01:20.556
they did not discover his body for one month.

01:01:20.905 --> 01:01:23.355
Because there's no family feeling, nothing,

01:01:24.326 --> 01:01:27.074
even a rat doesn't enter that house. Can you imagine!

01:01:30.418 --> 01:01:32.663
This is what has happened in thinking,

01:01:32.730 --> 01:01:35.408
“I am separated, I am individualistic.

01:01:35.475 --> 01:01:38.602
I am exclusive”. If you are really individualistic,

01:01:39.046 --> 01:01:41.046
if you are really mature, individually,

01:01:41.998 --> 01:01:45.339
then you know the unity much better.

01:01:46.630 --> 01:01:49.271
Then you understand that you are the support

01:01:50.148 --> 01:01:54.631
of the whole because you are so matured.

01:01:56.638 --> 01:01:58.638
No wonder our children are not maturing.

01:01:59.345 --> 01:02:01.345
They are behaving in such a manner.

01:02:02.090 --> 01:02:05.501
We are responsible, we must accept that in our own

01:02:06.867 --> 01:02:09.913
ideas about compatibility and all this nonsense,

01:02:09.923 --> 01:02:11.711
we don’t have in India, we are quite comfortable,

01:02:11.721 --> 01:02:13.606
we are producing children quite all right.

01:02:15.085 --> 01:02:21.662
We have no problems. Why do you run after these capricious,

01:02:22.444 --> 01:02:24.444
these shallow ideas?

01:02:26.432 --> 01:02:28.432
You will be held responsible

01:02:29.874 --> 01:02:33.861
for all these horrible diseases that men and women have got,

01:02:34.361 --> 01:02:36.361
and the children that are going to suffer,

01:02:36.861 --> 01:02:41.388
if you have charity, better start it at home.

01:02:42.980 --> 01:02:44.447
Better be charitable

01:02:44.571 --> 01:02:46.947
to your own wife and to your own husband.

01:02:47.447 --> 01:02:49.926
Be charitable to your children.

01:02:50.012 --> 01:02:52.460
Don't go by concept of falling in love,

01:02:52.678 --> 01:02:54.678
you'll fall, really and make others fall too.

01:02:56.176 --> 01:02:59.293
It's a concept, just a concept.

01:02:59.793 --> 01:03:03.235
I think some of these horrible people must have given you this concept.

01:03:04.526 --> 01:03:05.996
If you really fall in love

01:03:06.082 --> 01:03:08.082
how do you get up to marry another person?

01:03:09.147 --> 01:03:11.598
You fall, marry another person,

01:03:12.249 --> 01:03:14.249
again ready to marry another person.

01:03:14.316 --> 01:03:15.886
You are holding the hand of a person

01:03:15.952 --> 01:03:17.953
who is suppose to be your beloved or whatever it is,

01:03:17.979 --> 01:03:19.979
and looking at another one.

01:03:21.063 --> 01:03:24.788
This concept is absolutely wrong. You have to grow in love.

01:03:27.567 --> 01:03:29.567
As your own child is

01:03:29.672 --> 01:03:32.834
in the same way is your companion. They are two parts

01:03:33.503 --> 01:03:34.641
of one chariot.

01:03:35.273 --> 01:03:37.922
One is the left and other is the right. They're not

01:03:38.930 --> 01:03:40.930
unequal, they're equal

01:03:40.997 --> 01:03:44.212
but they are not similar, they have their own role.

01:03:44.505 --> 01:03:47.040
And women have to take their role courageously,

01:03:48.011 --> 01:03:50.647
to be the mother, as I always say, look at me.

01:03:51.448 --> 01:03:55.506
I am a Mother and in no way,

01:03:56.797 --> 01:03:58.797
in any way, I cannot think

01:03:59.128 --> 01:04:01.128
I could be anything better than this.

01:04:04.208 --> 01:04:06.509
Now if I start thinking, Oh God,

01:04:06.651 --> 01:04:08.840
I am a Mother all right, but

01:04:09.340 --> 01:04:11.340
I must know how to drive,

01:04:12.311 --> 01:04:15.663
then I'm finished. I must know how to drive a bus,

01:04:16.370 --> 01:04:18.370
I must know how to drive a train!

01:04:18.908 --> 01:04:20.022
What is the need?

01:04:21.351 --> 01:04:23.598
I saw one photographer who came to see me.

01:04:23.759 --> 01:04:25.332
He was supposed to take my photograph

01:04:25.380 --> 01:04:27.380
and whole hands were fill with blisters.

01:04:27.880 --> 01:04:29.921
I said first let me cure your blisters.

01:04:29.950 --> 01:04:31.457
How you are going to take my photograph?

01:04:31.788 --> 01:04:34.660
I said what have you been doing with your, photography?

01:04:34.727 --> 01:04:37.434
No, he said, this, I went to a forest

01:04:37.633 --> 01:04:39.633
and I cut some trees. I said, for what?

01:04:39.982 --> 01:04:43.086
You are a photographer, your hands are soft and deft

01:04:43.530 --> 01:04:45.792
why do you want to kill the deftness of your fingers?

01:04:46.292 --> 01:04:49.222
He said, no we must do other things also. I said, why must you?

01:04:50.833 --> 01:04:52.852
You see the nose doesn’t do the work of the eyes

01:04:52.900 --> 01:04:54.900
and the eyes do not do the work of the ears.

01:04:55.400 --> 01:04:58.730
Why must you do, your hands are all finished! And this is what it is.

01:05:00.548 --> 01:05:03.047
To us we feel that men are great

01:05:03.152 --> 01:05:06.001
so we start saying, "let's do the man's work."

01:05:08.384 --> 01:05:10.914
The man thinks, why "should women be like this?"

01:05:10.981 --> 01:05:12.214
You are companions -

01:05:12.883 --> 01:05:16.376
you are eternal companions. You are two

01:05:18.383 --> 01:05:20.910
beautiful wheels of a chariot.

01:05:22.201 --> 01:05:24.201
This is to be grown

01:05:24.419 --> 01:05:25.912
and to be matured within you.

01:05:26.130 --> 01:05:27.862
And when this centre is out,

01:05:28.136 --> 01:05:31.285
you get the problems of this centre

01:05:31.371 --> 01:05:34.076
by which you get asthma, tuberculosis,

01:05:35.593 --> 01:05:37.593
and the breast troubles.

01:05:37.622 --> 01:05:41.228
Men get asthma, very serious asthma and

01:05:41.257 --> 01:05:42.934
other problems of the lungs

01:05:43.001 --> 01:05:46.515
and ultimately, also lung cancer can develop.

01:05:48.748 --> 01:05:51.087
When you work too hard with the right hand side,

01:05:51.135 --> 01:05:54.406
you are ego orientated, that is ego develops too much,

01:05:54.473 --> 01:05:56.473
then your left side is neglected,

01:05:56.502 --> 01:05:59.286
you become unemotional, that time

01:05:59.409 --> 01:06:01.409
your heart gives a signal, you get a heart attack.

01:06:02.982 --> 01:06:04.982
When you do too much sometimes

01:06:05.444 --> 01:06:07.846
you may escape the heart attack, but you may get

01:06:07.951 --> 01:06:09.247
a  brain paralysis.

01:06:13.174 --> 01:06:16.115
We are bent upon destroying ourselves.

01:06:16.238 --> 01:06:19.751
The destruction is going to come from within, not from without.

01:06:21.400 --> 01:06:24.533
Those people who are try to shock you, this will happen,

01:06:24.581 --> 01:06:27.168
that the sun is doing this, this is nothing.

01:06:27.517 --> 01:06:30.184
It's all within you, the destruction has started.

01:06:30.684 --> 01:06:33.976
You are facing it because

01:06:34.476 --> 01:06:37.838
you cannot accept it.

01:06:39.110 --> 01:06:40.429
You have to accept

01:06:41.682 --> 01:06:43.708
that this is a challenge, I am not

01:06:43.737 --> 01:06:46.336
going to allow myself to be destroyed by foolish and stupid

01:06:46.365 --> 01:06:47.631
ideas that are around.

01:06:49.299 --> 01:06:52.097
And then in your own estimation and glory

01:06:52.597 --> 01:06:55.472
you will be surprised. After realisation

01:06:55.482 --> 01:06:57.673
you will be enriched but

01:06:57.740 --> 01:06:59.626
without Realisation, I don't know,

01:06:59.712 --> 01:07:02.768
it becomes a lecture and a lecture, just a brainwash.

01:07:03.626 --> 01:07:05.626
That beautiful thing should happen to you,

01:07:05.975 --> 01:07:09.472
and once you find your beauty within yourself,

01:07:09.520 --> 01:07:11.878
overnight I have seen people changed.

01:07:12.529 --> 01:07:14.529
Overnight it happens

01:07:15.029 --> 01:07:18.388
and I hope that will happen to you tonight.

01:07:18.888 --> 01:07:22.133
Today I have talked to you about this centre

01:07:22.633 --> 01:07:25.276
and later on I will be talking to you about

01:07:25.682 --> 01:07:28.099
two other centres which are here and here.

01:07:28.317 --> 01:07:30.317
And the Realisation that takes place,

01:07:30.817 --> 01:07:32.817
out of the limbic area,

01:07:33.034 --> 01:07:35.634
in the fontanel membrane,

01:07:35.910 --> 01:07:38.491
which is called as the Brahmarandra in Sanskrit language.

01:07:38.991 --> 01:07:40.991
Thank you very much. May God bless you.

01:07:42.546 --> 01:07:45.086
If you have any questions you please ask me.

01:07:47.488 --> 01:07:50.351
But questions should be something

01:07:50.822 --> 01:07:52.989
which are helpful, not some sort of

01:07:53.026 --> 01:07:54.883
quarrel. I am not here to quarrel with you.

01:07:55.214 --> 01:07:57.927
If you don't want your Realisation I am not going to force you.

01:07:58.427 --> 01:08:02.766
Please do not plead for any other organisation or any other guru,

01:08:03.266 --> 01:08:06.393
because I am not interested. I am only interested in you,

01:08:06.743 --> 01:08:08.743
I see that sparkle in you,

01:08:08.816 --> 01:08:11.684
that's why I am only interested in you, I'm not bothered about others.

01:08:12.184 --> 01:08:14.636
So you do not try to bring others ideas

01:08:14.837 --> 01:08:16.663
that this guru has said this or this

01:08:16.683 --> 01:08:18.446
one has said that and this is in the book.

01:08:19.308 --> 01:08:21.910
The proof of the pudding is that you haven't got your Realisation.

01:08:21.940 --> 01:08:23.940
If you have got it then you can go out.

01:08:26.064 --> 01:08:28.609
If you are sure you have got it, I don't want to force it on you.

01:08:28.724 --> 01:08:30.445
There's no quarrel about anything.

01:08:30.731 --> 01:08:32.731
There's no election on, nothing.

01:08:32.975 --> 01:08:34.184
You cannot give me anything.

01:08:34.235 --> 01:08:37.299
There's no shopping. It's a temple, you have come for a blessing.

01:08:37.799 --> 01:08:40.752
All right? Now you can ask the questions. Thank you very much.
